        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Minimize latency by implementing asynchronous processing and batching requests where possible. Use caching mechanisms (e.g., Redis) for frequent or repeated queries to reduce model load. Monitor API response times and scale horizontally with auto-scaling groups to handle traffic spikes. Additionally, optimize network latency by deploying model instances in regions close to your user base."
