        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Deploy comprehensive monitoring using tools like Prometheus or Grafana to track metrics such as error rates, latency percentiles, and resource utilization. Implement health checks and circuit breakers to isolate failures. For critical services, design fallback strategies, such as routing requests to a backup model or returning cached responses, to maintain uptime during outages or performance degradation."
